{"tid":1439362,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"Hong Kong is not a place, it's a people.","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:34:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T05:39:25.000Z","uid":284147,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb632afc1bd70099c2b4d721539ab50733499e1a","tid":1439362,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:34:43.000Z","msg":"香港係地圖只係一點，面積1100平方公里。<br />\n<br />\n下一輪各行各業要表態嘅， 係讚成/反對搵一個新嘅1100平方公里建立新香港。自制真普選。<br />\n<br />\n香港人表態後再決定下一步， 有冇it人可以起個網站/app， 建立一個新國家需要乜人材建立乜野設施，有冇表態左嘅人係呢個field。 食水 電 基本野實走唔甩。<br />\n<br />\n國際社會幫唔到香港人因為地理上香港係大陸嘅一部分， 但搵一個1100平方公里嘅新地點， 佢地應該幫得到。<br />\n<br />\n無真香港人嘅香港， 就留返俾大陸自己慢慢玩死佢。<br />\n<br />\n無論係邊有香港人就會係香港。"},{"pid":"a85761af95717fe1fffb56ed3a2904bf5822dc86","tid":1439362,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"仲搞港獨俾位人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d279609a98a32b03f90a9c4e51bfa3567f621a36","tid":1439362,"uid":284147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a85761af95717fe1fffb56ed3a2904bf5822dc86","tid":1439362,"uid":142854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:35:48.000Z","msg":"仲搞港獨俾位人入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:38:09.000Z","msg":"完全唔覺得係港獨。 <br />\n<br />\n係香港人大遷移。"},{"pid":"895bfcddab7ddfc5c43ad3f3d50185965273d728","tid":1439362,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:39:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}